%{! 
Adapted from the case study on [Typed combinators soundness and completeness](/wiki/typed-combinators-soundness-and-completeness/).

## Syntax

!}%
% lambda calculus
%sort term %.
%name term %.
%term app %pi term %-> term %-> term %.
%term lam %pi (%pi term %-> term) %-> term %.
% combinator calculus
%sort comb %.
%name comb %.
%term s comb %.
%term k comb %.
%term i comb %.
%term capp %pi comb %-> comb %-> comb %.
%{! 

